	<h1 class="title">“冰桶挑战”不是一时狂欢，这一年里它真的帮助了渐冻人</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/998/small/998.jpg?1402274915" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐云路 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-04 19:15:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/14451/medium/14451.jpg?1441353440" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


